rule Bypass_Sample
{
    meta:
        description = "Evasion bypass rule targeting multiple exit paths"
        cape_options = "bp0=$pattern0+0,action0=skip,bp1=$pattern1+0,action1=skip,bp2=$pattern2+0,action2=skip,count=0"

    strings:
        $pattern0 = { E8 C8 FFFFFF ?? }  # 6 bytes: Call instruction with displacement
        $pattern1 = { FF7508 E8C8FFFFFF ?? }  # 9 bytes: Push and call
        $pattern2 = { E8C8FFFFFF 8B45 ?? }  # 6 bytes: Call followed by mov eax, dword ptr [ebp+8h]

    condition:
        any of them
}
